{"tid":1887051,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"中國傳媒報導: 猶戴．偉浚即將加盟中甲球會深圳佳兆業｜5年必入中國隊","createTime":"2020-02-19T09:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T10:31:07.000Z","uid":9030,"like":4,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"f4ab89e75f671d8e2ddba9c70d844bf664af711b","tid":1887051,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:47:59.000Z","msg":"【不買國腳造國腳！深圳從馬體、狼隊挖人<br />\n<br />\n鄧納東尼對戴偉浚特別認可，隊內傳出&ldquo;戴偉浚5年必入國足&rdquo;的聲音<br />\n<br />\n目前，戴偉浚已被鄧納東尼拍板，獲得通知參加球隊下階段冬訓，轉會只差正式簽下合同了。<br />\n<br />\n深圳隊今年有非常多的年輕球員前來試訓，戴偉浚脫穎而出。<br />\n<br />\n通過英國、西班牙多名球探介紹，戴偉浚比中甲最佳新人徐越還要出色。<br />\n<br />\n深圳隊簽下他也是考慮球隊長遠發展，並有意在未來打造擁有數名中國成年國腳的陣容班底。"},{"pid":"effebc040f69d191412f16410611110239cc67b1","tid":1887051,"uid":33053,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:52:34.000Z","msg":"支那人踢支那球隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa79ddb18b9659e6947cdc4c2bb8eaf0b2541e5","tid":1887051,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"effebc040f69d191412f16410611110239cc67b1","tid":1887051,"uid":33053,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:52:34.000Z","msg":"支那人踢支那球隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:54:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fd754571f21e7f4b314cbf21de00f0e8132854","tid":1887051,"uid":127143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:56:49.000Z","msg":"咁勁都冇得踢中超？"},{"pid":"5800456ab7c7f5bcc580e3f72c5ab70c5c8ba799","tid":1887051,"uid":117402,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:58:22.000Z","msg":"有英超狠隊唔踢, 返中甲?<br />\n.....真係愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"064d57fc4b431fa5425d66ed1f8f33c0ca6ac3b0","tid":1887051,"uid":72045,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:58:29.000Z","msg":